<div style="position:absolute;left:38.40px;top:636.54px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">1.  </span><span class="cls_008">例</span><span class="cls_007">：  </span><span class="cls_008">論文を</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">書きます・資料を</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">集めて</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">います</span></div>
