<div style="position:absolute;left:104.40px;top:718.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">弁護士に</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">なります・法律を</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">勉強する</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">つもりです</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_009">→</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:106.80px;top:734.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">だい  がく いん</span></div>
