<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:758.94px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">“</span><span class="cls_008">名詞の</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">ために</span><span class="cls_009">”</span><span class="cls_008">也表示</span><span class="cls_009">“</span><span class="cls_008">為了成為名詞的利益</span><span class="cls_009">”</span><span class="cls_008">的意思。如</span><span class="cls_009">（</span><span class="cls_008">④</span><span class="cls_009">）</span><span class="cls_008">。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:779.34px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">〔註</span><span class="cls_007">1</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:84.60px;top:779.34px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">〕第</span><span class="cls_007">36</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:124.20px;top:779.34px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">課學的「</span><span class="cls_007">～</span><span class="cls_008">ように</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:229.80px;top:779.34px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">」也用在表示目的上</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">但是相對於用「</span><span class="cls_007">～</span><span class="cls_008">よう</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:799.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">に」時要使用非意志動詞</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">用「</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:236.40px;top:799.74px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">～</span><span class="cls_008">ために」時則要使用意志動詞</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">試比較以下</span></div>
