<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:85.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">①是自己有意識地以</span><span class="cls_009">“</span><span class="cls_008">擁有店舖</span><span class="cls_009">”</span><span class="cls_008">為目的</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">為了實現這個目標</span><span class="cls_009">“</span><span class="cls_008">正在存錢</span><span class="cls_009">”，</span><span class="cls_008">相</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:106.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">對地</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">⑤</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:104.40px;top:106.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">表示以</span><span class="cls_009">“</span><span class="cls_008">能擁有店舖</span><span class="cls_009">”</span><span class="cls_008">這樣的狀態作為目標</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">為了接近這個狀態而</span><span class="cls_009">“</span><span class="cls_008">正</span></div>
