<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:371.34px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">⑧</span><span class="cls_006">この</span><span class="cls_012">  </span><span class="cls_006">はさみは</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">花を</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">切るのに</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">使います。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:78.00px;top:393.60px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">這把剪刀用在剪花。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:186.00px;top:408.54px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">おお</span></div>
